metadata.title: General Land Use - EVOS Database

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), Interagency Shoreline Cleanup Committees (ISCC)

metadata.description: Data Type: Exxon Valdez Oil Spill;  Miscellaneous land use has been collected from ISCC Response map. These locations give a rough estimate of locations but are not inclusive. The purpose for this effort was to identify and protect key habitats and fishing areas during the initial response phase of the spill.
